@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vxmoyo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.60) / (v2 + 0.47 / tmp + 0.94)) * 0.64)
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos(v0))
    tmp = v1
    v2 = 0.85
    v1 = v0
    tmp = wp.exp(((v0 + 0.64 - tmp + 0.75) + 0.18))
    v0 = wp.abs((wp.abs(v1 + 0.85) + (tmp + 0.56 + tmp + 0.02)))
    data[tid] = v0
